      "source": "String a1 = new String(\"aa\");\r\nString a2 = new String(\"aa\");\r\nString a4 = a1;\r\na4=\"aa\";\r\nIO.println(a4==a1);\r\nString a3 = \"aa\";\r\na3=a1;\r\nIO.println(a1==a2);\r\nIO.println(a1==a3);\r\nIO.println(a1.equals(a3));\r\n\r\na1 = a1+a3;\r\nIO.println(a1);\r\n\r\nInteger b1 = new Integer(1);\r\nInteger b2 = new Integer(1);\r\nInteger b3 = 1;\r\nint b4=1;\r\nIO.println(b4==b3);\r\nIO.println(b1.equals(b3));\r\n\r\nb2 = b1+b2;\r\nIO.println(b2);\r\n\r\nInteger a = 128; \r\nInteger b = 128;\r\nIO.println(a==b);\r\n",
